RE CP ChangeHi Stephanie I just wanted to be sure you received the documents I sent you on Sequent I was also wondering where we stand If you could let me know I would appreciate it Thanks Leigh Original Message From Panus Stephanie Sent Tuesday October PM To Hayman Kendra Subject RE CP Change Kendra Can you send me the documents that you have Thanks Stephanie Panus Senior Legal Specialist Enron Wholesale Services Smith Street EBC Houston Texas ph fax email Original Message From Hayman Kendra Sent Tuesday October PM To Panus Stephanie Subject CP Change Hi Stephanie I work in deal confirmation and have been receiving confirms back from Sequent Energy Management The are saying thay it should be Sequent Energy Management LP not LLC We were wondering if you have recieved documentation of this We have documentation of this if you need it Please let me know if you reflect this or not Thanks Leigh
